Package org.jdesktop.swingx.color

Class ColorUnit

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Color
org.jdesktop.swingx.color.ColorUnit
All Implemented Interfaces:
Paint, Transparency, Serializable
public class ColorUnit extends Color
A color is either a keyword or a numerical specification. The keywords aka color names are ASCII case-insensitive.

See www.w3.org/TR/css-color-3 .

Author:
homeb
